Package fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.specialized

package fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.specialized
This package is highly dependent on the SPMF library developed by Philippe Fournier Viger. We offer a layer of abstraction to efficiently exploit his algorithms and classes. If you wish to know more about SPMF you can visit this page
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app
    Core package containing all chocominer modules and features.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.specialized.experiences
    Contains all the experiences for specialized data mining.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.specialized.factories
    Package containing the factory design pattern allowing for an easier management of the creation of solving strategies.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.specialized.strategies
    Package containing solving strategies, used in the SPMFIMExperience.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.parsers
    Package containing parsers, which parse different types of external data structures from external libraries into a homogenous data structure and extract only the useful information from said data structures.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.solutions
    Package containing modules allowing to return a homogenous type of data mining solutions for outside service to use.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.stats
    This package contains classes that provide useful statistics for the database the mining will be performed on.
